  <title component="profesor"><nbsp/>([@@@@@@@@@] mins)</title>

  <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
  <p>Display equations from the first problem in the last activity.</p>
<p><q>¿Como usaron lo que saben sobre decenas y unidades para resolver los problemas?</q> (Some questions I saw I could just count by 10 on the graph because the scale was 10. We didn’t subtract all at once. We subtracted the tens, then the ones. We were thinking about how to get to the next ten to make adding the tens easier.)</p>
<p><q>En el futuro, ¿cómo podrían usar la estrategia ‘Tres lecturas’ solos, sin ayuda de un compañero?</q> (We could use it any time by thinking what the problem is about. We can read the problem to look for what can be measured or counted in the problem. We can read it to think about strategies we could use to solve the problem.)</p>

</subsubsection>



